esent overshoot of this\ntarget CO2 is not brief, there is a possibility of seeding irreversible\ncatastrophic effects.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 7 Apr 2008 20:16:55 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 18 Jun 2008 21:38:01 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Wed, 15 Oct 2008 21:51:55 GMT"}],"update_date":"2008-11-13"}
