 surface field. From our observations, we infer that\na rotation period lower than ~12 days is necessary for the toroidal magnetic\nenergy to dominate over the poloidal component.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 8 Apr 2008 14:39:02 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 5 May 2008 14:08:16 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Thu, 10 Jul 2008 12:30:31 GMT"}],"update_date":"2008-10-14"}
